==English==
=== Noun ===
'''brush''' ([[brushes]])

# An [[implement]] with a handle, and a head with multiple more or less flexible [[bristle]]s, used for any of various purposes including [[clean]]ing, [[paint]]ing, and arranging [[hair]].
# A spring-loaded electrical contact that connects the [[rotor]] and [[armature]] of a motor or generator.
# The act of brushing something.
#: ''She gave her hair a quick brush.''
# ''(uncountable):'' Wild [[vegetation]], generally larger than grass but smaller than trees.
# The tail of a fox.

