=== Transitive verb ===
'''brush'''

#To clean with a brush.
#: ''Brush your teeth.''
#To untangle or arrange with a brush.
#: ''Brush your hair.''
#To apply with a brush.
#: ''Brush the paint onto the walls.''
#To remove with a sweeping motion.
#: ''Brush the flour off your clothes.''
